V0034_01_00_00_0.text: I play every game out there, and I win 'em all!

V0034_01_00_01_0.text:
Of course I'll Duel!
Duel Monsters is one of my faves!

V0034_01_00_02_0.text: I heard you're a world-class talent.

V0034_01_00_02_1.text: But I'll be the judge of that!

V0034_01_00_03_0.text: Yugi, let's see who's the real King of Games!

V0034_01_00_04_0.text: If I win, you’ll do whatever I say for a week. Deal?

V0034_01_00_05_0.text:
You want to Duel?
I didn't think you even knew the rules...

V0034_01_00_06_0.text: Having a Millennium Item doesn't make you a Dueling expert!

V0034_01_00_07_0.text: I get to Duel the creator of Duel Monsters?

V0034_01_00_07_1.text:
Wow!
This is an honor, Mr. Pegasus!

V0034_03_00_04_0.text: Now this is what I call a Duel!

V0034_05_00_00_0.text: If I don't draw the right card, I'll lose...

V0034_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my face-down card!

V0034_08_00_00_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Summon Dice!

V0034_08_00_02_0.text: I activate the Equip Spell, Fairy Meteor Crush!

V0034_08_00_04_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Dimensionhole!

V0034_08_00_05_0.text: I equip Cyclon Laser on Gradius!

V0034_08_00_06_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Power Capsule!

V0034_08_00_07_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Dicephoon!

V0034_08_00_08_0.text: My monster doesn't like going to the Graveyard alone.

V0034_08_00_08_1.text: I activate the Trap Card, Michizure!

V0034_08_00_09_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Safe Zone!

V0034_08_00_10_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Dice Re-Roll!

V0034_08_00_11_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Dragon Laser!

V0034_08_00_12_0.text: My Continuous Trap Card, Blind Destruction!

V0034_08_00_14_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Blind Obliteration!

V0034_08_00_15_0.text: I activate my Continuous Trap Card, Dice-nied!

V0034_08_00_17_0.text: I activate the Continuous Trap Card, That Six!

V0034_08_00_18_0.text: I activate the Continuous Trap Card, Diceversity!

V0034_09_00_00_0.text: I activate D.D.M. - Different Dimension Master's effect!

V0034_09_00_01_0.text:
Check this!
Orgoth the Relentless's effect!

V0034_09_00_06_0.text: Lord British Space Fighter's effect activates!

V0034_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0034_13_00_01_0.text:
Whoa! D.D.M.?!?
Dungeon Dice Monsters?
...Oops, no.

V0034_13_00_03_0.text:
This is D.D.M.'s strongest monster!
I dimension the dice!

V0034_13_00_12_0.text: Fire your jets, Victory Viper XX03!

V0034_13_00_15_0.text:
Lord British Space Fighter!
Blast off!

V0034_13_00_18_0.text:
Blue Thunder T-45!
On the scene!

V0034_13_00_24_0.text: I Special Summon an Option Token!

V0034_13_00_25_0.text: I Special Summon a Multi Token!

V0034_13_00_26_0.text: I Special Summon a Thunder Option Token!

V0034_14_00_01_0.text:
I strike fast and hard!
Let's battle!

V0034_16_00_01_0.text:
The end is here!
I win!

V0034_19_00_03_0.text:
Orgoth!
Show 'em why you're called relentless!

V0034_19_00_12_0.text:
Victory Viper XX03!
Launch your attack!

V0034_19_00_15_0.text:
Lord British Space Fighter!
Launch your attack!

V0034_19_00_18_0.text:
Blue Thunder T-45!
Launch your attack!

V0034_21_00_00_0.text: There's no way you can make a comeback.

V0034_28_00_00_0.text: No matter the game, I never lose!

V0034_28_00_01_0.text: You're not just second best, you're second rate!

V0034_28_00_02_0.text: It's impossible to defeat me in any game!

V0034_28_00_03_0.text: You lost because you missed the finer points of this Duel.

V0034_28_00_04_0.text: I'm gonna enjoy having an obedient dog for the next week.

V0034_28_00_05_0.text:
Not bad for a first-timer.
But you never had a chance.

V0034_28_00_06_0.text: Pegasus, would you like to give my game a try?

V0034_29_00_00_0.text:
The better player won today.
And it was you.

V0034_29_00_01_0.text: I may have lost, but I sure had a good time losing!

V0034_29_00_03_1.text:
...No, of course you didn't.
You beat me fair and square.

V0034_29_00_04_0.text:
Well done, Yugi.
I may have lost, but no regrets.

V0034_29_00_05_0.text:
I need a moment...
I can't believe I lost to an amateur...

V0034_29_00_06_0.text:
Wow, Mai.
Not bad at all.

V0034_29_00_07_0.text: It'll take a miracle to defeat the creator of this game.

V0034_30_00_00_0.text: Don't you know when to give up?

V0034_30_00_01_0.text: I don't think anything I did was unfair.

V0034_30_00_02_0.text: When it comes to Dueling, you're a natural!

V0034_34_00_00_0.text: If you lose, you gotta do whatever I say for a week!

V0034_34_00_01_0.text: You oughta pay more attention to your weak points.

V0034_34_00_02_0.text: Wow! You pulled off a high level strategy!

V0034_34_00_04_0.text: Argh... I can't figure out this puzzle!

V0034_35_00_00_0.text: Duel Monsters is one of my favorite games!

V0034_35_00_01_0.text: You'll crown me the King of Games!

V0034_36_00_02_0.text: Well... It's all in your hands!
